you can see here the 3 equations in question

28
00:02:52.270 --> 00:02:59.270
for the most complicated one, there is a cubic root here

29
00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:05.280
and here a power of a cubic root, and a square root

30
00:03:05.290 --> 00:03:10.290
so we have a solution with nested radicals

31
00:03:10.300 --> 00:03:25.300
the second equation, a little simpler, and here again we have a solution that involves only  square roots

32
